Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mindfusion.scheduling.model.Command
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddItemCommand, ChangeItemCommand, CompositeCommand, RemoveItemCommand

    public abstract class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an action that changes the schedule and whose effects can be undone.

        protected abstract boolean execute()
        Description copied from class: Command
        Carries out an action that changes the schedule in some way.

        Commands, which return false are never recorded in the command history.

        Returns:
        true, if the command actually caused changes in the schedule; otherwise, false.
